        PERSON_ROLE,
        MAJOR,
        AGE,
        CHANGE_FLAG,
        CHANGE_REASON,
        HAS_SALARY_INPUT 
    FROM
        SRPMS_PROJECT_PERSON_JOIN 
    WHERE
        PROJECT_ID = ? 
        AND JOIN_WAY = ?
